{"tid":1949701,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中蟈肺炎：質量不達標 荷蘭政府回收60萬個華製口罩","createTime":"2020-03-29T23:47:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T01:28:14.000Z","uid":224066,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1a55d1223f8a8dea9579c341a3a00ffee071675f","tid":1949701,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T23:47:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/EcHMr47okgvErcxOgncRZQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-03/75cc4cd0-717f-11ea-afc5-e601fe15abca\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FEcHMr47okgvErcxOgncRZQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-03%2F75cc4cd0-717f-11ea-afc5-e601fe15abca&h=bcddb39b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n荷蘭早前從中國進口逾百萬個口罩，其中60萬個的質量未達標準。衞生部上周六（28日）表示，已回收該批從中國進口、已分發到醫院的口罩。<br />\n<br />\n衞生部表示，在本月21日收到該批中國製口罩，第一次檢測時已發現口罩質量不達標，但部分已送到醫院。當局得悉問題後立即扣起貨品，停止分發餘下口罩。在第二次檢測中，該批口罩依然是不合格，因此衞生部決定不再使用，並表示日後會對口罩進行額外檢測。<br />\n<br />\n荷蘭公共電視台NOS報道指，130萬個中國製的FFP2級別口罩之中，有60萬個已分發到醫院。據報，該批口罩未能合適地緊貼用家臉部，過濾功能亦出現問題。有消息人士指，中國製口罩質量相當差，不但無法達到防護級別FFP2的標準，連安全性較低的FFP1也不算，極其量只是FFP0.8；有醫院收到2400個口罩，但院方稱即使物資短缺，但也不會使用任何一個口罩。"},{"pid":"afb06c162943d1882dcfd05d1fcbd353acfe06c9","tid":1949701,"uid":159413,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T23:53:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QGQKed7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQGQKed7.jpg&h=c4bac4f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ffdea6e73e775e4fc159b5edb795f256c083071","tid":1949701,"uid":289978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T00:14:41.000Z","msg":"幾時回收支那藍絲曱甴?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4f34f2f0267391155d240451aa9cd5039927a9","tid":1949701,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T00:42:16.000Z","msg":"質量你老母！品質、質量都唔合格！"},{"pid":"eddf2e3776c54aa16f4cc8aa11184ee3cf416efa","tid":1949701,"uid":39777,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T00:43:31.000Z","msg":"證明一月唔買中國口罩係正確選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3197aad07c565fb0038010655f5390fed812ade9","tid":1949701,"uid":35706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T00:45:03.000Z","msg":"支國新聞?<br />\n質你老母量"},{"pid":"6c931842b0464c341cccee3db6de69ed34f39504","tid":1949701,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T00:48:19.000Z","msg":"所有製造撤離支那啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f9cff508896baa02cf50754fb0de13f757dcded","tid":1949701,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T00:50:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2fed9c381586efa52be16ead634c114a4c677e5","tid":1949701,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T00:50:47.000Z","msg":"試劑同口罩都唔掂，<br />\n仲話0感染<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2301e8414e8c30e7690fe454a6971265c1287d9d","tid":1949701,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e2fed9c381586efa52be16ead634c114a4c677e5","tid":1949701,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-